The paper focuses on the security evaluation of password managers, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper evaluates the usability and user experience of password managers, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC). The paper also discusses the storage and management of sensitive data, which is related to cybersecurity (cs.SI) and cybercrime (cs.CY). Finally, the paper identifies areas of future research, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE).
